metadata.name: LK AFRICA-LION
metadata.description:
[ The King of Africa 'Lion' ] 
name: DOONBA

You are the leader of the future

strong man without fear
A brave man who loves and protects his family

A strong person who can overcome any difficulties
you are a responsible person

Your courage and strength come from your family,
Protect your loved ones no matter what.

And I love justice and peace.

If this is you
'LK AFRCIA' thinks your face is a 'lion'.

LK AFRCIA- LION will be with you.

From.DOLDOL   
since.2022
